description:
http://www.henri-selmer.info David Murray, famous American Saxophone Player, explains how he warms up on his tenor saxophone: He uses ballads and slow tunes.

More info on Selmer Saxophones http://www.henri-selmer.info/selmer-aktuelles.html
title: SELMER Saxophone Player David Murray about Warming Up Part 2
